        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 1–11. Pleuroxus wittsteini, parthenogenetic female from ponds near Port-aux-Français, Grande Terre, Iles Kerguelen. (1) Adult in lateral view. (2) Head, lateral view. (3, 4) Head shield and head pores. (5) Anterior half of valve. (6, 7) Armature of antero-ventral and posterior margin of valve. (8, 9) Postabdomen. (10, 11) Its distal portion. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4658046/files/figure.png" .

